verses.text:
Meet a-gain, we are go-ing to meet a-gain;
Meet a-gain where part-ing nev-er comes;
Meet a-gain where sin-ners joy We shall meet with-out de-lay;

Meet a-gain, we are go-ing to meet a-gain;
Meet a-gain where part-ing nev-er comes;
Meet a-gain where sin-ners joy We shall meet with-out de-lay;

Meet a-gain, we are go-ing to meet a-gain;
Then our friend-ship will be pure and sweet;
Then our love will glow with heav-en-ly light,
And we nev-er more shall part.
